Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.54,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:52.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:06.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please... kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:16.29,Default-alt,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.61,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just staring out into space for, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.60,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There are people inside of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They want our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,No! They're monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:44.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.64,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.16,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,They're monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:50.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.95,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Give me back my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.23,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Stop it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.11,Default-alt,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.77,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.58,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.39,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.86,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.57,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, bring it over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.42,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.16,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it over by the waste plant earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.68,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, it was with some huge guy in an armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.69,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the one from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:21.19,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive him for kidnapping Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.36,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Demon! Devil! Loincloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.87,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There she is! Shao Ma-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.75,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.63,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,That fat one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.82,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, they called him a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.87,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Their regeneration ability matches that of an immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.78,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We can't jump in carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.35,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance! Let's go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.11,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. He's not an easy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.82,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Why are those two together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:12.98,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.81,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,This place... is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:19.08,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a feeling that something was out of place, ever since I arrived in this country, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.69,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:27.57,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There are things crawling beneath my feet... and a lot of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.46,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've thought something like this was under Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.17,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,That was done by the gatekeepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gatekeepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.45,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,They won't attack you if you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's something up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do we still have a long way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.00,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,A long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He knows where people go after you swallow them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:45.00,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Father knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... You're alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A red... stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Envy's core.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:30.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,After all the time we spent looking for one,\Nthere's one right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out, Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together, Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.68,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.63,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,They are chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.54,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.47,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.65,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... there's something beneath us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.04,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Are they chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.27,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.31,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Father made us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.65,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Lust, and Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.51,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,It's loud up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.50,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:39.11,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember my parents' names, their faces, or even my own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.93,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't remember if I was abandoned or sold before I had even been given a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:50.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you will lead this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.07,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We were called the "Führer President Candidates".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:03.08,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,And we were all gathered into one place and educated in many different fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.91,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How to be a good emperor, anthropology...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:11.46,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We were trained in military combat, marksmanship, and swordsmanship until we were highly capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:33.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He was just a pawn for you to achieve your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.44,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,"I will lead this country someday."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,With that thought in mind,\NI endured the toughest of trainings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He was no good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.75,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.29,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?! Those bodies are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.85,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is the twelfth one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.99,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,...who will receive my wrath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:38.62,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone is a high energy substance that includes the souls of many humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:44.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,As it enters a human's body, it goes on a rampage and tries to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:56.26,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction and reconstruction by the stone is repeated until either the body dies or wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.37,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:03.01,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,A new species of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.11,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.35,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,You've been selected to be the man who will lead this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.62,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,He will prepare everything you may need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.01,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,From this day on, your name shall be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.84,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,King Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:25.80,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,All that was left was a soul and the emotion of wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:35.00,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if this soul belongs to someone who was turned into the stone, or if it was mine to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:48.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you were human, couldn't you live as a human instead of a Homunculus, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to go back to being a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.46,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,This body has far surpassed human capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.16,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It's far superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:09.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Just as how you humans are proud to be human,\Nwe are proud to be Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:14.68,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that woman took that pride to her death, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Just something temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I've collected all the ones around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all from Xerxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's a portion of the mural that was in a temple in the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:45.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a transmutation circle for a philosopher's stone, like the one beneath Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The sun represents the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The moon represents the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And this stone which has the mural on it. This represents the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.30,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... explain it so I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:03.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, what was drawn there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is a circle for human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.11,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Human transmutation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.28,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,So that means, to raise the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:11.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:15.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The principle of alchemy is equivalent exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:19.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,One cannot create a soul that doesn't exist in this world, at least through alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've thought of a way to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What if I transmute myself from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A human that's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.17,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Transmute from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:41.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I use this transmutation circle to decompose myself, then put myself back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's also human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The gate should open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If Gluttony is a fake Gate of Truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:53.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't we be able to get to\Nthe real world by going through the real gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:58.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open the gate; you guys leap in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.73,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What if this doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then we suffer from rebound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All of the effects of the rebound go to the one who attempted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.88,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing about alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:19.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So, Envy, there's something I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:27.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The mural I saw at Xerxes looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about this symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:34.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's the word representing God, but flipped over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And the dragon with two heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:40.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This represents the perfect being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:46.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This means "I will cast God from the Heavens to the Earth, and become the perfect being."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.45,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,People think of outrageous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wonderful if they had only thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The problem here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...this part, which is broken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A lion that swallows the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This represents the philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And the ingredients of philosopher's stones are live humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Envy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:15.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the nation of Xerxes,\Na nation so prosperous, perish overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where did its citizens go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:22.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't a portion of the ruins in here to cover up the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:30.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You guys turned all of Xerxes' citizens into a philosopher's stone, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who transmuted themselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:52.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who turned all of the country's people into a philosopher's stone for tremendous power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...for the sole purpose of becoming a being that would surpass God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the "Father" that you talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:06.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that guy trying to recreate that event in this country by using you guys, the Homunculi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.96,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:16.89,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop beating around the bush, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:21.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You need a toll if you're going to open the gate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.29,Default-alt,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,These are all people from Xerxes, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:42.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx97}Their bodies and minds have rotted away in the ancient past, and they are beings who are solely used as an energy source.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.43,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even remember what they used to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sympathizing with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:56.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}The sole reason you want to think of them as humans is that you want to believe that your brother, who's only a soul, is human, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:04.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You hesitate to set fire to coal because you feel sorry for a tree that died ages ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.64,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They can't return to being human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:13.00,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Lay down a definition for a human with logic and not emotion, alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:20.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:28.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin, if something happens to me,\Ntell everyone about what these guys are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:33.20,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens to Amestris isn't my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.30,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There are people precious to you waiting for you in that country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here alive and tell them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:52.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please let me use your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:05.43,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that pose of putting their hands together looked similar to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a prayer to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd open it again... under this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin! Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.94,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.82,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same sensation I felt while being swallowed by Gluttony...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:08.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The body and the soul are connected by the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:13.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A part of my body is before the Gate of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:18.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I just let my mind guide me,\NI should be able to get to the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:24.53,Default,Truth,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you didn't come here to get your body back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is through here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:34.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can find clues on how to find my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there two gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Al!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:08.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll come and bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:04.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx94}It is hard to find the shape of an illusion, like a wavering flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:09.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}And a flame can be cruel at times, but can also be a flame of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:15.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:19.68,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 27, Banquet at the Crevice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:24.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't be afraid of the darkness inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
